{
  "stem": "11882.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And these were a series of interviews, you might say, with the questions taken out about his life-- which was a very interesting life.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I took a section of a little over 100 pages, and have the good fortune to have an English book coming out, a little book-- not intended for sale, but for the family and maybe for some of the prosecutors that knew him, and don't have his German language book because we are in America, after all.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in his book, he tells what Nuremberg meant to him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And if you look at it, he lived Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Before the-- we heard of Nuremberg, before Hitler came to power, he was fighting Nazism.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nazism didn't just come from today to tomorrow, but developed, got its grip on different localities, different voting areas.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was fighting-- at that time, he was in Berlin in the employ of the Interior Ministry and the Justice Ministry of the pre-Hitler government, the Weimar Republic.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he failed in his effort to get Hitler prosecuted and kicked out of the country as a dangerous foreigner.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hitler was an Austrian to begin with, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he failed in that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as Hitler came in, he's riding along with his dear mother, the bacteriologist-- she rode in with him to work to Berlin every day-- and starts crying as she sees all the swastikas and says, now the pogroms will come to us.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His mother felt it coming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was terribly hard for her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Her son, her other son, had already gone to America.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a physician.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he had all of these German employees.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
